<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/28/%e4%bd%9b%e6%95%99%e7%95%8c%e6%84%9b%e5%bf%83%e6%8e%a5%e5%8a%9b-%e7%82%ba%e8%8a%b1%e8%93%ae%e5%a5%87%e8%b9%9f%e7%8d%b2%e6%95%91%e5%a5%b3%e7%ab%a5%e3%80%8c%e5%b0%8f%e6%b2%82%e3%80%8d%e9%bb%9e%e4%ba%ae/">佛教界愛心接力 為花蓮奇蹟獲救女童「小沂」點亮希望之光</a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="687" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827048.jpg?resize=1220%2C687&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-273677" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827048.jpg?w=1706&amp;ssl=1 1706w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827048.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827048.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827048.jpg?resize=390%2C220&amp;ssl=1 390w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">▲小沂的勇氣感動全台，三位長老法師捐贈20萬元慰問金作為生活與學習補助，並贈大熊娃娃與禮物。（圖／記者莊全成翻攝）</figcaption></figure>



<p>記者 莊全成／花蓮報導</p>



<p>佛教界今（28）日於花蓮光復高工舉辦「馬太鞍溪堰塞湖受災戶慰助金發放活動」，現場湧入上千名災民，活動除發放慰助金外，並提供1,200份便當與生活物資、皂福公司捐出100箱洗衣精，場面溫馨感人。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="687" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827032.jpg?resize=1220%2C687&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-273681" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827032.jpg?w=1706&amp;ssl=1 1706w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827032.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827032.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827032.jpg?resize=390%2C220&amp;ssl=1 390w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">▲佛教界募集1,180萬元善款與物資，於花蓮光復高工舉辦「馬太鞍溪堰塞湖受災戶慰助金發放活動」。（圖／記者莊全成翻攝）</figcaption></figure>



<p>花蓮馬太鞍溪堰塞湖溢流重創花蓮光復鄉，災後傳出年僅六歲女童「小沂」奇蹟獲救的感人故事。她在洪水暴漲中被姑姑、姑丈托上屋頂倖存，困屋兩日後終獲救，成為災區希望的象徵。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="687" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827050-1.jpg?resize=1220%2C687&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-273684" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827050-1.jpg?w=1706&amp;ssl=1 1706w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827050-1.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827050-1.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/S__271827050-1.jpg?resize=390%2C220&amp;ssl=1 390w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">▲小沂的勇氣感動全台，三位長老法師捐贈20萬元慰問金作為生活與學習補助，並贈大熊娃娃與禮物。（圖／記者莊全成翻攝）</figcaption></figure>



<p>小沂的勇氣感動全台，台灣佛教總會、中華佛教比丘尼協進會及屏東縣佛教會三位長老法師宏安長老尼、常露長老尼、釋見引法師──共同捐贈20萬元慰問金，作為生活與學習補助，並親贈大熊娃娃與禮物，陪伴她走出創傷。</p>



<p>儀式中，小沂抱著比她高的熊娃娃說：「謝謝法師阿姨，我會乖乖念書，也要像姑姑一樣勇敢！」童言童語感動全場。宏安長老尼回應：「孩子能平安，就是最大的福報，妳的勇氣是大家的榜樣</p>



<p>釋見引法師表示：「愛無分地域，願這份關懷陪伴孩子迎向光明。」小沂母親含淚致謝，感激佛教界以慈悲之心點亮希望，讓災後家庭在愛與祝福中重獲力量。</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/28/%e4%bd%9b%e6%95%99%e7%95%8c%e6%84%9b%e5%bf%83%e6%8e%a5%e5%8a%9b-%e7%82%ba%e8%8a%b1%e8%93%ae%e5%a5%87%e8%b9%9f%e7%8d%b2%e6%95%91%e5%a5%b3%e7%ab%a5%e3%80%8c%e5%b0%8f%e6%b2%82%e3%80%8d%e9%bb%9e%e4%ba%ae/">佛教界愛心接力 為花蓮奇蹟獲救女童「小沂」點亮希望之光</a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
